p combo through the many upgrades and customisation options available as you venture deeper into the ruins via your chosen path.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452070/extras/fffee9ff41b81a699f8008c18ae67d6d.webp?t=1770306561\" width=610 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452070/extras/12cf956803903da979ebe27eb27662f2.poster.avif?t=1770306561\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452070/extras/12cf956803903da979ebe27eb27662f2.webm?t=1770306561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452070/extras/12cf956803903da979ebe27eb27662f2.mp4?t=1770306561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Looking for a different challenge? Take on the Survival mode for a timed, wave-based game mode. How long can you survive against the rising difficulty and increasingly tougher foes?",
